#!/usr/bin/env python
"""
CESMLC V9 - daily inference with post-model RCA/reference enrichment
====================================================================

Clean separation:
1. ML scores temporal/behavioral engineered features.
2. RCA/reference enrichment runs after model scoring and only on abnormal/review rows.
3. Final report is grouped by PRIMARY_ANOMALY_CLUSTER and PRIMARY_ABNORMAL_FEATURE.
"""
